  "industry_note": "Plansee Mo-Re (Mo-41Re or Mo-47Re) — 'Rhenium effect' alloy. Re 첨가로 BCC→HCP solid-solution → ductility boost (DBTT 낮추기) + recrystallization 저항 + creep 우수. σy 720-900 / UTS 1000-1200 / El 30% (RT ductile, pure Mo 의 brittleness 해소). E 360 GPa. Tmax 1400°C continuous in inert (1600°C short). 사용: 우주 (nuclear thermal rocket nozzle, RTG thermocouple), high-T thermocouple type C (W-5Re vs W-26Re), 가속기 target, ion source. 가격 매우 비싸 (Re 60% — $300-500/kg).",
